# üß† NeuroIndex

[![Tests](https://github.com/Umeshkumar667/NeuroIndex/actions/workflows/tests.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/Umeshkumar667/NeuroIndex/actions/workflows/tests.yml)
[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/neuroindex.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/neuroindex)
[![Python 3.9+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.9+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Code style: black](https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-black-000000.svg)](https://github.com/psf/black)

**NeuroIndex** is a **production-ready vector memory system** for AI applications.

> üåü **Community Edition** - Free & Open Source under MIT License

## ‚ú® Features

- ‚ö° **FAISS vector search** - Fast similarity matching
- üíæ **SQLite persistence** - Durable storage
- üîÑ **LRU cache** - Frequently accessed items
- üìä **Built-in metrics** - Observability
- üîí **Thread-safe** - Concurrent reads

Perfect for **RAG systems**, **AI agents**, **chatbots**, and **semantic search**.

---

## üì¶ Community Edition Limits

| Feature | Community (Free) | Pro ($49/mo) |
|---------|-----------------|--------------|
| Documents | 10,000 max | **Unlimited** |
| Embedding Dimension | 384 only | **Any dimension** |
| Semantic Graph | ‚ùå | ‚úÖ |
| Batch Insert | ‚ùå | ‚úÖ (15x faster) |
